VIOLENCE: - Establishment of Unique SOS line - Awareness raising campaign including focus on Roma women - Establishment centralised data base for cases of violence within Social Card - Conduct annual assessments of knowledge, awareness and attitudinal change - Develop a training module and provide training for elementary and secondary school teachers and psychologists on preventing and combating violence in family;
POLITICS: - Ensured interactive cooperation with identified entities on political empowerment of women in EU countries - Prepared and conducted promotion and advocacy of the affirmative actions, taking into consideration lessons learned by local, regional and international partners - Established a network of interested NGOs and CSOs for the political empowerment of women - Advocacy campaign on ammending Electoral Law, Law on Political Parties and Law o Financing of Political Parties - Visibility actions - Evaluation
ECONOMY - Strengthened capacities of the existing infrastructure in 4 pilot municipalities through on-job training of local employees and enabled continuous advice and support to entrepreneurs - Strengthened capacities of local community and civil society organizations (local NGOs and media) to raise public understanding and support to women entrepreneurship, to help in motivating potential entrepreneurs, to support networking, etc. - Promotional activities - Match making event between financial institutions and women entrepreneurs

